data.eml:eml: The taxonomic identity of some enigmatic darkling beetle genera: Archinamaqua Schawaller, 2012 and Menederopsis Koch, 1954 (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae) from Namaqualand, South Africa

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kamiński, Marcin J., Schawaller, Wolfgang (2019): The taxonomic identity of some enigmatic darkling beetle genera: Archinamaqua Schawaller, 2012 and Menederopsis Koch, 1954 (Coleoptera: Tenebrionidae) from Namaqualand, South Africa. Zootaxa 4543 (2): 291-294, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4543.2.8
